parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the Takata airbag inflator can cause the airbag to explode, resulting in serious injury or death.
symptoms: The airbag warning light illuminates
the airbag compartment is deformed or bulging
the airbag cover detaches from the dashboard.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the ABS can cause extended brake pedal travel, increasing the risk of a crash.
symptoms: The brake pedal goes to the floor
the brake pedal intermittently depresses to the floorboard
the vehicle takes longer to stop.
